            <th scope="col" class="text-center" style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); vertical-align: middle;">Sales Volume (30D)</th>
            <th scope="col" class="text-center" style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); vertical-align: middle;">Floor Change (30D)</th>
